            <li><a href="#instructions" rel="modal:open">Instructions</a>
                <div id="instructions" class="modal">
                    <p><h4>Welcome to Bryant's Tic-Tac-Toe, a.k.a. Jim-vs-Jim.</h4><br>
                    <b>General Assembly</b> is opening up a new campus. <b>Jim1</b> & <b>Jim2</b> are trying to make life for themselves as convenient as possible by nabbing <u>3 consecutive rooms</u> that are either in the same row, column, or diagonal.  Whoever gets that combination wins the game, otherwise it's a tie!  Best of luck teachers!</p>
                    <a href="#" rel="modal:close">Close</a>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li><a href="#gameboard">Play</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
